-- Saudi Samba Financial Group proposes H2 div of 0.7 riyal
-- By Nadia Saleem
-- Sun Dec 28, 2014 01:21AM EST
-- None



DUBAI, Dec 28 (Reuters) - Saudi Arabia's Samba Financial Group <1090.SE> proposed a dividend of 0.7 riyals (18.7 cents) per share for the second half of 2014, it said in a bourse statement on Sunday.

